SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

CREATE TABLE "RefreshTokens" (
    "Id" character varying(450) NOT NULL,
    "Token" character varying(500) NOT NULL,
    "UserId" character varying(450) NOT NULL,
    "ExpiresAt" timestamp with time zone NOT NULL,
    "IsRevoked" boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE,
    "RevokedAt" timestamp with time zone,
    "ReplacedByToken" text,
    "CreatedAt" timestamp with time zone NOT NULL,
    "UpdatedAt" timestamp with time zone,
    "CreatedBy" text,
    "UpdatedBy" text,
    CONSTRAINT "PK_RefreshTokens" PRIMARY KEY ("Id"),
    CONSTRAINT "FK_RefreshTokens_AspNetUsers_UserId" FOREIGN KEY ("UserId") REFERENCES "AspNetUsers" ("Id") ON DELETE CASCADE
);

2025-10-25 12:23:33.786 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (134ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1

    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"

2025-10-25 12:42:13.921 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (22ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."AssetId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AssetTag", a."Condition", a."ItemId", a."Location", a."Name", a."PoNumber", a."ProjectId", a."SerialNumber", a."Status"
    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

SELECT t."Id", t."AssetTag", t."Name", t."SerialNumber", t."Status", t."Condition", t."Location", t."PoNumber", i."Name", p."Name", COALESCE((
    SELECT e1."AssignedDate"
    FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."AssetId" AND e1."Status" = 1
    LIMIT 1), TIMESTAMPTZ '-infinity'), t0.c, t0."FirstName", t0."LastName", t0.c0
FROM (

    FROM "Assets" AS a
    ORDER BY a."AssetTag"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Items" AS i ON t."ItemId" = i."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."AssetId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."AssetId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."AssetId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeAssets" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1
    WHERE t1.row <= 1
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AssetId"
ORDER BY t."AssetTag"

    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"

ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-25 13:12:06.324 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (22ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-25 13:15:52.197 +03:00 [INF] Successfully handled GetNationalitiesQuery
2025-10-25 13:15:52.192 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (

    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

    WHERE p."CompanyId" = c."Id") AS "ProjectCount", (

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

2025-10-25 16:01:20.141 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

    WHERE e."CompanyId" = c."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"

2025-10-25 16:09:57.716 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

2025-10-25 16:18:17.377 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (13ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Code", t."Name", t."Description", t."Status", CASE
    WHEN c."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN c."Name"
    ELSE ''
END AS "CompanyName", c0."Name" AS "CostCenterName", n."Name" AS "NationalityName", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM "Employees" AS e
    WHERE e."ProjectId" = t."Id") AS "EmployeeCount"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CompanyId", p."CostCenterId", p."Description", p."Name", p."NationalityId", p."Status"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    ORDER BY p."Name"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Companies" AS c ON t."CompanyId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "CostCenters" AS c0 ON t."CostCenterId" = c0."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Nationalities" AS n ON t."NationalityId" = n."Id"
ORDER BY t."Name"

) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."SoftwareName", t."LicenseKey", t."LicenseType", t."Seats", t."Vendor", t."PurchaseDate", t."ExpiryDate", t."Cost", t."Status", t."PoNumber", p."Name", COALESCE((

    FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e1
    WHERE t."Id" = e1."SoftwareLicenseId" AND e1."Status" = 1

FROM (

    FROM "SoftwareLicenses" AS s
    ORDER BY s."ExpiryDate"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."ProjectId" = p."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1.c, t1."FirstName", t1."LastName", t1.c0, t1."SoftwareLicenseId"
    FROM (
        SELECT TRUE AS c, e0."FirstName", e0."LastName", 1 AS c0, e."SoftwareLicenseId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY e."SoftwareLicenseId" ORDER BY e."Id", e0."Id") AS row
        FROM "EmployeeSoftwareLicenses" AS e
        INNER JOIN "Employees" AS e0 ON e."EmployeeId" = e0."Id"
        WHERE e."Status" = 1
    ) AS t1

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."SoftwareLicenseId"
